# Notification System

## Overview

This project is a full stack notification platform developed as part of the AffordMed assessment.

The system supports:
- Fetching notifications from protected APIs
- Sorting notifications based on priority
- Filtering notifications by category
- Logging middleware integration
- React frontend rendering
- Responsive notification display

---

# Tech Stack

## Frontend
- React
- Vite
- Vanilla CSS

## Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js
- Fetch API

---

# Features

- Protected API integration using Bearer Token
- Notification priority sorting
- Top 10 notifications display
- Filter notifications by type
- Logging middleware
- Query parameter support
- Responsive frontend UI

---

# Notification Priority

Notifications are sorted in the following order:

1. Placement
2. Result
3. Event

If priorities are same, latest notifications are displayed first.

